						               													<description>Modderfontein 1901 is an Ascari Scenario and it has to be played with Ascari rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the Second Boer War, the Commandos tactics in guerrilla managed to continue the war, even if the capital cities of the Boer Republic had fallen.&amp;#10;Commandos led by intrepid and young leaders started to harass the British lines of reinforcements and the Empire responded with flying Corps with Mounted Cavalry and the internment of the Boers non combatants into concentration camps.&amp;#10;The Boers decided then to raid directly Cape Colony, where several Boers lived and partake for the Republics; Jan Christian Smuts led the most daring raid.&amp;#10;In the attempt to cross Elands River, the short for ammunition and supplies Boers decide to attack the 17th Lancers camp near Modderfontein, managing to surrender the Lancers and loot the camp... the bitter end is still far away!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Will you manage to loot the camp and replenish your supplies or will you be defeated by the Empire?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;27 gorgeous counters, a colorful A4 map and English rules wait for you!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
